OL,3,CChild poverty strategy 'Isn't going to
OL,4,Ccut it' says children's commissioner
OL,6,FWith almost one in three children in
OL,7,FWales living in poverty, the Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment's new strategy to tackle
OL,9,Fthe issue has been labelled as
OL,10,F"disappointing" by Wales' .
OL,12,FRocio Cifuentes says the strategy
OL,13,Fneeds to be "more than a list of good
OL,14,Factions and intentions".
OL,16,FShe told ITV Wales how strong calls
OL,17,Fwere made with other "authoritative
OL,18,Forganisations" to deliver a clear plan
OL,19,Fof action, but she feels the document
OL,20,F"doesn't seem to have listened."
