OL,6,FShe says they "stuff paper in their
OL,7,Fshoes on a wet day".
OL,9,FMs Cifuentes says the Welsh government
OL,10,Fstrategy "doesn't show how clearly it
OL,11,Fis going to track its own progress".
OL,13,FShe added: "You know there is a list
OL,14,Fof commendable actions and policy
OL,15,Finitiatives, contained within that
OL,16,Fstrategy but so many authoritative
OL,17,Fvoices have said that a really
OL,18,Feffective child poverty strategy needs
OL,19,Fto be much more than a 'list of good
OL,20,Factions and intentions'.
