OL,6,F"And it isn't at the moment."JShe
OL,7,Fissued a statement on Tuesday (23
OL,8,FJanuary) in collaboration with 14
OL,9,Fother national leading children and
OL,10,Fpoverty expert organisations.
OL,12,FShe says the Welsh government often
OL,13,Fsays they "don't hold all the levers
OL,14,Fto reduce and eradicate child poverty."
OL,16,FMs Cifuentes continued: "While that is
OL,17,Ftrue to an extent. They don't control
OL,18,Fwelfare benefits, they don't control
OL,19,Ftaxation.
